Haul data set 2

Source: R/Data.R
haul2.Rd

A data set containing the counts of five species of fish from the NOAA Pacific Trawl Data, 1999-2004. Depth, lattitude, and longitude are also included.

haul2

Format

A data frame with 1072 rows and 5 variables:

year

year data was collected

depth

depth that fish count was recorded, in meters

lattitude

lattitude was fish count was recorded, in degrees

longitude

longitude was fish count was recorded, in degrees

Sebastolobus.altivelis

count of Sebastolobus altivelis species

Sebastolobus.alascanus

count of Sebastolobus alascanus species

Antimora.microlepis

count of Antimora.microlepis species

Coryphaenoides.acrolepis

count of Coryphaenoides acrolepis species

Alepocephalus.tenebrosus

count of Alepocephalus tenebrosus species
